article_text:
Carrollton, GA (30117)

Today

A mix of clouds and sun. High 89F. Winds light and variable..

Tonight

Partly cloudy skies during the evening giving way to a few showers after midnight. Low 64F. Winds light and variable. Chance of rain 30%.

article_metadata.description: Toby and Adele are dressed as Thing 1 and Thing 2 Saturday during the Carroll County Humane Society’s annual Fun Dog Show. They won first runnerup during the best costume
article_metadata.author: Melanie Boyd/Times-Georgian
